arket and nonexistent at auction.) But, this person reported, =E2=80=9Cthe =
auction houses are offering deals that are based upon [anticipation of] a m=
oderate to strong seller=E2=80=99s market=E2=80=9D in the fall, particularl=
y in the sub-$5 million market. Anecdotes aren=E2=80=99t data, but the deal=
er was moderately optimistic: =E2=80=9CThe short-term indicators from my ti=
ny sample seem to portend a stronger fall season.=E2=80=9D</li></ul><br/><b=
